      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="titoleto"><a name="d3e8685"> </a>Refitting the front footpegs
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/note.jpg">Note
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8688"> </a>Refitting of the front RH footpeg is described in detail; the LH footpeg can be removed following the same procedure.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8691"> </a>Position spring (4) so that the end (A) rests on the footpeg (3).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8693"> </a>Position footpeg (3) inserting the end (C) of spring (4) in the hole (D) of the frame plate.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8695"> </a>Fit pin (2) as shown.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8697"> </a>Lock pin using circlip (1).
         </div>
      </div>
